'''沙赫娜茲·巴列維'''公主（{{lang-fa|'''شهناز پهلوی'''}}，{{lang-en|'''Princess Shahnaz Pahlavi'''}}，{{bd|1940年|10月27日|catIdx=Pahlavi, Shahnaz}}）是[[伊朗|伊朗]]未代皇帝[[穆罕默德·礼萨·巴列维|穆罕默德·礼萨·巴列维]]和首任皇后 [[埃及|埃及]]公主[[茀絲亞·福阿德|茀絲亞]]唯一的女兒。<ref>[http://iranian.com/main/blog/darius-kadivar/royal-beauty-princess-shahnaz-pahlavi-1960s-70s.html "Royal Beauty: Princess Shahnaz Pahlavi (1960's/70's)"] {{Wayback|url=http://iranian.com/main/blog/darius-kadivar/royal-beauty-princess-shahnaz-pahlavi-1960s-70s.html |date=20141103202031 }}. Iranian. Retrieved 10 October 2012.</ref><ref>[http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=L5cyAAAAIBAJ&sjid=gucFAAAAIBAJ&pg=4011,5239480&dq=shahnaz+pahlavi&hl=en "A quick look at the Shah's life"]. Lawrence Journal. AP. 28 July 1980.</ref>公主有四個同父異母的弟妹，包括皇太子[[禮薩·巴列維|禮薩·巴列維]], 以及两名同母异父的弟妹。透過她母親，沙赫娜茲亦是埃及國王[[法鲁克一世|法鲁克一世]]的姪女及[[福阿德二世|福阿德二世]]的表姐。

她擁有[[切尔卡斯亚|切尔卡斯亚]]人、[[波斯人|波斯人]]、[[法國|法國]]、[[阿爾巴尼亞人|阿爾巴尼亞人]]及[[阿塞拜疆族|阿塞拜疆族]]的血統；並在瑞士接受教育。<ref>[http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=2QokAAAAIBAJ&sjid=2AQEAAAAIBAJ&pg=1824,1472649&dq=ardeshir+zahedi&hl=en "Only child of Shah of Iran will marry in simple rites"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=2QokAAAAIBAJ&sjid=2AQEAAAAIBAJ&pg=1824,1472649&dq=ardeshir+zahedi&hl=en |date=20211214063146 }}.  Ocala Star Banner (Tehran). AP. 10 October 1957.</ref>在1979年[[伊朗伊斯蘭革命|伊朗伊斯蘭革命]]後，公主一直在瑞士定居。<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/1384839.stm "Shah's daughter 'could not stand' exile"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/1384839.stm |date=20141129034309 }}. BBC. 12 June 2001.</ref>

